sequenceDiagram
    actor H as Host
    participant FE as Frontend (Lobby)
    participant BE as Backend (ws_host)
    actor PL as Players

    Note over H,PL: Host is in Lobby phase (game not yet started)
    H->>FE: sets time limit input to 30
    FE->>FE: validates (10 ≤ value ≤ 60)
    FE->>BE: set_time_limit {seconds: 30}
    BE->>BE: session.time_limit_sec = 30
    BE-->>H: time_limit_set {seconds: 30} (BroadcastAll)
    BE-->>PL: time_limit_set {seconds: 30} (BroadcastAll)
    Note over BE: limit locked once game starts<br/>each question countdown uses session.time_limit_sec
